   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_fargeau.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-2-" mid="70" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Don't you worry about that. Trust is of utmost importance to merchants. <BR>'Til we meet again, traveller from a far away land.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-a" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Oh... <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you've brought my brother's letter!<BR>
I can't wait to read how he's doing!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-b" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>………….<BR>……………… Phew….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-c" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Is there something bad?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-d" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>N-no…….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-e" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>…He just wrote he's doing well so he wants me to take care of Hiver and other siblings… and that he's sending money to Hiver every month and asked if it's enough… He says he's going to send more next time… so that I can… go and buy some snacks... and he wrote... he knows how tough working in a dye factory is hard so I should take care of myself... (Grele sobs)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-f" mid="77" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Merca is a free city but the taxes here are really high… But my brother said we can live like humans here compared to other Childs' estates… So he left to work as a slave labourer and has been sending us money to support us... He used to study hard to become a merchant before our parents became ill... He was preparing to work in the trader's union in Merca's Heart….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-g" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Sis probably didn't show me his letters because she knew I'd weep like this… I know I shouldn't cry but… I just feel so sad...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-h" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele${sound:npc_Grele_9710_qu_01.ogg}<BR>……Is… Is <FONT color=#a82424>Lagendia</FONT> really a peaceful and harmonious place?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-i" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(How should I put it? That world isn't all rainbows and ponies too...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-j" mid="81" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Mistlanders always say that <FONT color=#a82424>Lagendia</FONT> is nothing but <FONT color=#a82424>Goddess Altea's dream</FONT> which can be broken anytime and we call them our shadow… They say Lagendians are like phantoms so they try to take our bodies to take a real form. But Hiver told me it's all a farce created by the Vestinel Order.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-k" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>That's right. It's the people in Lagendia who are worried about an attack from Mistland. I'm here to stop that.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-l" mid="83" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele${sound:npc_Grele_9710_qu_02.ogg}<BR>……So it really is Goddess Vestinel's fault, isn't it? Look at my hands… They have become so black because of the dye. What do I get for working so hard for the whole day?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-m" mid="84" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>They say it's right to snatch what we want from others. It's a sin to be weak. But some people are just born strong and some weak. I don't want to hurt anyone or steal anything. But that means I'm weak and that makes me a sinner.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-n" mid="85" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>I don't want to be bad! Being bad doesn't make everyone happy either! Both Mistlanders and Lagendians are being tortured because of Goddess Vestinel's greed… Maybe I should just accept this world for what it is...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-o" mid="86" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>But Guy is working for us who are weak… He could have abandoned us like the guys in other families, but he didn't...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-p" mid="87" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…Yeah, there's one thing I can tell you for sure.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-q" mid="88" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Neither you nor your brother is a sinner.<BR>On the contrary, you're doing a very good job, Grele.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-r" mid="89" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>…….Thanks, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>…Maybe I... I just wanted to hear that...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-s" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>……Ah, my brother said boys shouldn't cry… Hehe… I'm sorry for acting like a child…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-2-t" mid="91" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Let it out when you're down. Don't keep it inside.<BR>(He's making me miss Rubinart and Geraint…)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-2-t" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-3" mid="92" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Grele$<BR>Oh! I left the factory for too long. I need to go now!<BR>Thank you again, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. I hope we can meet again soon!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1825_wind_grele-3" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_grele.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1825_wind_grele-3-" mid="94" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Grele smiles as he waves. I have more things on my mind now. It would be good if Merca could help the weak… First, I should go to </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT><FONT color=#662500> and discuss with him.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" mid="95" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I told you to stay low. What are you doing here?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>……Merca is not even a Child's land but why are the taxes so high? You said true neutrality is achieved by standing on the side of the weak!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" mid="97" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No way!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" mid="98" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It's because you're the only one I can turn to. Did I offend you?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" mid="99" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're such a good-looking man, I want to keep staring at you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" mid="100" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Vernicka, I know you're much older than you look...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka looks dumbfounded.)</FONT><BR>Are you being mistaken that since I look your age, you're thinking of me as a casual friend to chat with or something...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" mid="101" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Relying on someone and being rude are completely different. You seem confused about the two.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" mid="102" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>………Tsk. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka seems to think you're pathetic.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-f" mid="103" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Anyway, you've just made a very rude comment. You've made me a tyrant who extorts taxes from the people.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-g" mid="105" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I feel like a frog in front of a snake. Should I have thought twice before spitting out those words?!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-h" mid="106" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>But it's fine. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka shrugs his shoulders nonchalantly.)</FONT><BR>It's not a wrong thing to collect high taxes in Mistland.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-i" mid="107" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>……?! Why…? But if people can't pay their taxes… That would make everyone's life worse.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-j" mid="108" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Of course. Those who can't pay taxes end up in jails or become slaves… or run away to the wastelands… When they do that, they might want to blame someone or bear hatred for the world. But it's their fault for not being able to earn enough money to pay tax. It's a sin to be incapable.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-k" mid="109" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Nonsense! What are you talking about…?!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-l" mid="110" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9710_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Whatever it is, the <FONT color=#a82424>Childs</FONT> are the only ones who are at the peak of our society. To fight them, one has to be someone from the royal family that existed even before the Childs appeared, or have special talents like me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-m" mid="111" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>This place is a free city, nothing more. It's not a social welfare state that aims to help the poor. Being neutral applies only on conflicts and not on every single person in this city.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-n" mid="112" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>The people who want to live in <FONT color=#a82424>Merca</FONT> despite the high taxes are those who know that they can at least rise in ranks when they work hard. I've already told you before that the strong and the weak are also judged based on intangible stuff too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-o" mid="113" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Look at yourself. You're absolutely at a disadvantage in rising to the top in Mistland, but you're standing here before me after proving your worth. If you're unhappy with the tax policy, become the President with your own abilities to change it. That would make you realise how much money goes in to keep this city running when its resources are nothing but goldstones.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-p" mid="114" select_type="2" />
